<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;">}</span></span></code></pre></div><h3 id="gmeventservice" tabindex="-1">GmEventService <a class="header-anchor" href="#gmeventservice" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;GmEventService&quot;">​</a></h3><h4 id="what-is-it-2" tabindex="-1">What is it? <a class="header-anchor" href="#what-is-it-2" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;What is it?&quot;">​</a></h4><p>The <code>GmEventService</code> can be used to trigger an <code>onEvent</code> callback any time an order is created, modified, or canceled on the Galactic Marketplace.</p><div class="info custom-block"><p class="custom-block-title">INFO</p><p>The <code>GmEventService</code> is implemented by the <code>GmOrderbookService</code> and is how its internal state of the marketplace orderbooks is kept up-to-date</p></div><h4 id="example-1" tabindex="-1">Example <a class="header-anchor" href="#example-1" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;Example&quot;">​</a></h4><div class="language-typescript vp-adaptive-theme"><button title="Copy Code" class="copy"></button><span class="lang">typescript</span><pre class="shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark vp-code" tabindex="0"><code><span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583;">import</span><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;"> { Connection, PublicKey } </span><span style="--shiki-light:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583;">from</span><span style="--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF;"> &#39;@solana/web3.js&#39;</span><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;">;</span></span>
